# Sentrux architecture check

Tourgo defines layers and boundaries in `.sentrux/rules.toml` (NeoUI SPA vs Friend app, import boundaries).

After edits under `public/js/`, `public/game/js/`, or `.sentrux/`, run from the **repository root**:

```bash
sentrux check .
```

Resolve reported violations before finishing the task. Install the CLI if needed: [Sentrux README (中文)](https://github.com/sentrux/sentrux/blob/main/README.zh-CN.md) (`brew install sentrux/tap/sentrux` on macOS).

**Baseline (phase 0):** `.sentrux/baseline.json` is committed; CI runs `sentrux gate .` after `sentrux check .`. When you intentionally accept a new architecture snapshot (e.g. after a large refactor), refresh the baseline from repo root: `sentrux gate --save .`, then commit `.sentrux/baseline.json`.
